        {
          "name": "create-solution",
          "description": "Press <enter> key to show commands...\nadd-target-framework\nAdd a target framework.\nbump-versions\nBumps the major, minor or patch version of the given projects. Only projects with GeneratePackageOnBuild set are being processed.\nchange-versions\nReplaces the entire version of the given projects. Only projects with GeneratePackageOnBuild set are being processed.\nclean\nDelete project's bin and obj directories.\nenable\nEnable a project feature.\nlist-projects\nLists all projects which are affected by project commands.\nnowarn\nAdd a no warn id to the projects.\nswitch-assemblies-to-projects\nUpdates assembly references to project references in the given projects.\ninstall-packages\nused-packages\nLists all used packages and their licenses.\nswitch-to-projects\nSwitch NuGet references to project references\nswitch-to-packages\nSwitch project references to NuGet references\nupdate-packages\nUpdates the versions of the selected package references in the given projects.\nnogitchanges\nassemblygen",
